  <entry>
    <title>Blockchain Seminar (Bug Injection on Smart Contract)</title>
    <link href="https://eveneko.com/2021/07/17/blockchain-seminar-20210717/"/>
    <id>https://eveneko.com/2021/07/17/blockchain-seminar-20210717/</id>
    <published>2021-07-17T20:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-19T01:57:17.934Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Speaker: Zhou Yu(俞州)</p><h1 id="Paper-1-How-Effective-are-Smart-Contract-Analysis-Tools-Evaluating-Smart-Contract-Static-Analysis-Tools-Using-Bug-Injection"><a href="#Paper-1-How-Effective-are-Smart-Contract-Analysis-Tools-Evaluating-Smart-Contract-Static-Analysis-Tools-Using-Bug-Injection" class="headerlink" title="Paper 1(How Effective are Smart Contract Analysis Tools? Evaluating Smart Contract Static Analysis Tools Using Bug Injection)"></a>Paper 1(<a class="link"   href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2005.11613" >How Effective are Smart Contract Analysis Tools? Evaluating Smart Contract Static Analysis Tools Using Bug Injection<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>)</h1><h2 id="Static-Analysis-Tools"><a href="#Static-Analysis-Tools" class="headerlink" title="Static Analysis Tools"></a>Static Analysis Tools</h2><ul><li>Symbolic Execution<ul><li>Oyente</li><li>Securify</li><li>Mythril</li><li>Manticore</li></ul></li><li>Pattern matching<ul><li>SmartCheck</li></ul></li><li>Static Single Assignment<ul><li>Slither</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="Bug-Injection"><a href="#Bug-Injection" class="headerlink" title="Bug Injection"></a>Bug Injection</h2><h3 id="Challenging"><a href="#Challenging" class="headerlink" title="Challenging"></a>Challenging</h3><ul><li>找个合适的插入位置<ul><li>编译不通过</li></ul></li><li>语义依赖<ul><li>时间戳(block.timestamp())（可以被矿工恶意利用）</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="Smart-Contract"><a href="#Smart-Contract" class="headerlink" title="Smart Contract"></a>Smart Contract</h3><ul><li>数量 50</li><li>类型</li><li>代码长度</li><li>插入方式<ul><li>插入完整代码(Inject full code snippets)</li><li>弱化安全机制(Weakening security mechanisms)</li><li>修改代码(Transform codes)</li></ul></li></ul><h3 id="Bug-Type"><a href="#Bug-Type" class="headerlink" title="Bug Type"></a>Bug Type</h3><ul><li>Reentrancy<ul><li>一个函数在同时多次调用</li></ul></li><li>Timestamp dependency<ul><li>依赖时间戳，被 矿工恶意利用</li></ul></li><li>Unhandled Send</li><li>Unhandled exceptions<ul><li>异常终止合约</li></ul></li><li>Transaction ordering dependency(TOC)<ul><li>打包区块，对用户交易顺序改变</li></ul></li><li>Integer overflow/underflow</li><li>Use of tx.origin<ul><li>合约相互调用时</li><li>tx.origin: 最初调用者</li><li>msg sender: 上一个调用者</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="Solidify-Algorithm"><a href="#Solidify-Algorithm" class="headerlink" title="Solidify Algorithm"></a>Solidify Algorithm</h2><ol><li>确认可以编译通过，生成抽象语法树，找所有可插入位置</li></ol><ul><li>插入完整代码(Inject full code snippets)<ul><li>一行代码</li><li>代码块（位置与function有关）</li></ul></li><li>弱化安全机制(Weakening security mechanisms)<ul><li>tx.origin</li><li>Integer overflow/underflow</li><li>delete checking</li></ul></li><li>修改代码(Transform codes)</li></ul><ol start="2"><li>插入漏洞</li><li>在静态分析工具上分析</li></ol><ul><li>正确性（类型，位置）</li><li>设定不同阈值，用来判断误报</li></ul><h2 id="Exploitability"><a href="#Exploitability" class="headerlink" title="Exploitability"></a>Exploitability</h2><ul><li>TOD测试代价较大，没有测试</li></ul><h2 id="Q-amp-A"><a href="#Q-amp-A" class="headerlink" title="Q&amp;A"></a>Q&amp;A</h2><ul><li>插入的漏洞和源代码没有关系</li></ul><h1 id="Paper-2-LAVA-Large-scale-Automated-Vulnerability-Addition"><a href="#Paper-2-LAVA-Large-scale-Automated-Vulnerability-Addition" class="headerlink" title="Paper 2(LAVA: Large-scale Automated Vulnerability Addition)"></a>Paper 2(<a class="link"   href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/abstract/document/7546498" >LAVA: Large-scale Automated Vulnerability Addition<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a>)</h1><p>自动收集漏洞</p><h2 id="Source"><a href="#Source" class="headerlink" title="Source"></a>Source</h2><p><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Eveneko/Source-Hosting/master/PicX/image.5qgkkhydsvg0.png"                      alt="image"                ></p><ul><li>Accident</li><li>Search</li><li>Injection</li><li>Synthesis</li></ul><h2 id="Taint-based-measures"><a href="#Taint-based-measures" class="headerlink" title="Taint-based measures"></a>Taint-based measures</h2><ul><li>被利用的数据，DUA（Dead, Uncomplicated And Available data）</li><li>TCN<ul><li>数字越大，变量被计算次数越多</li><li>0代表直接从输入来，我们认为更容易被控制</li></ul></li><li>liveness<ul><li>评估输入数据</li><li>输入被用在分支</li><li>决定分支越多，对程序控制流越大，越好被利用</li></ul></li></ul><h2 id="Attack-point-selection"><a href="#Attack-point-selection" class="headerlink" title="Attack point selection"></a>Attack point selection</h2><ul><li>在DUA出现之后，可以利用DUA，就是一个可以利用对位置</li></ul><h2 id="Data-flow-bug-injection"><a href="#Data-flow-bug-injection" class="headerlink" title="Data-flow bug injection"></a>Data-flow bug injection</h2><ul><li>在DUA和attack point之间建立Data-flow</li></ul><h2 id="Finding-DUA"><a href="#Finding-DUA" class="headerlink" title="Finding DUA"></a>Finding DUA</h2><ul><li>LAVA 大概的流程</li></ul><p><img                       lazyload                     src="/images/loading.svg"                     data-src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Eveneko/Source-Hosting/master/PicX/image.mff5f669nao.png"                      alt="image"                ></p><h1 id="实验室工作"><a href="#实验室工作" class="headerlink" title="实验室工作"></a>实验室工作</h1><ul><li>Vulnerability Detection Platform</li><li>因为缺少数据，所以想自己插入漏洞</li><li>bytecode，source code 两种数据的不同</li><li>跨平台</li></ul><h1 id="PDF"><a href="#PDF" class="headerlink" title="PDF"></a>PDF</h1><div class="row">    <embed src="/pdf/bug_injection.pdf" width="100%" height="550" type="application/pdf"></div><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/markmap.css" type="text/css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/spoiler.css" type="text/css"><script src="/js/spoiler.js" type="text/javascript" async></script>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Speaker: Zhou Yu(俞州)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;Paper-1-How-Effective-are-Smart-Contract-Analysis-Tools-Evaluating-Smart-Contract-Static-Analysis-Tools-</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
