go-base-interfaces/" title="Interfaces">Interfaces</a></h1><ol start="18"><li>Interfaces. I</li><li>Interfaces. II</li></ol><h1 id="-8"><a href="#-8" class="headerlink" title=""></a><a href="/2021/07/12/go-base-concurrency/" title="Concurrency">Concurrency</a></h1><ol start="20"><li>Introduction to Concurrency</li><li>Goroutines</li><li>Channels</li><li>Buffered Channels and Worker Pools</li><li>Select</li><li>Mutex</li></ol><h1 id="-9"><a href="#-9" class="headerlink" title=""></a><a href="/2021/07/12/go-base-object-oriented-programming/" title="Object Oriented Programming">Object Oriented Programming</a></h1><ol start="26"><li>Structs Instead of Classes</li><li>Composition Instead of Inheritance</li><li>Polymorphism</li></ol><h1 id="-10"><a href="#-10" class="headerlink" title=""></a><a href="/2021/07/12/go-base-defer-and-error-handling/" title="Defer and Error Handling">Defer and Error Handling</a></h1><ol start="29"><li>Defer</li><li>Error Handling</li><li>Custom Errors</li><li>Panic and Recover</li></ol><h1 id="-11"><a href="#-11" class="headerlink" title=""></a><a href="/2021/07/12/go-base-first-class-functions/" title="First Class Functions">First Class Functions</a></h1><ol start="33"><li>First Class Functions</li></ol><h1 id="-12"><a href="#-12" class="headerlink" title=""></a><a href="/2021/07/12/go-base-reflection/" title="Reflection">Reflection</a></h1><ol start="34"><li>Reflection</li></ol><h1 id="-13"><a href="#-13" class="headerlink" title=""></a><a href="/2021/07/12/go-base-file-handling/" title="File Handling">File Handling</a></h1><ol start="35"><li>Reading Files</li><li>Writing Files</li></ol><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/markmap.css" type="text/css"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/spoiler.css" type="text/css"><script src="/js/spoiler.js" type="text/javascript" async></script>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
